<@ULBP4M3LK> how are you including the files? You’ll need to use “require_css” and “require_js” in your modules. That will run the the files through the css and js processor.

More info here: <https://community.HubSpot.com/t5/CMS-Development/Our-website-CSS-file-is-not-minified-can-any-one-help-me-on-why/m-p/366561/highlight/true|https://community.HubSpot.com/t5/CMS-Development/Our-website-CSS-file-is-not-minified-can-any-one-help-me-on-why/m-p/366561/highlight/true>
